VIRTUAL - VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENT RUNS ON A PHYSICAL MACHINE
CONTAINER - ISOLATED ENVIRONMENTS THAT DON'T PULL THE OWN OS, JUST THE REQUIRED DEPS(LIGHWEIGHT)


## Redis -> is a db that stores data in RAM, provinding faster reads
## BullMq -> is a job queue library for Node.js that uses Redis to store and manage jobs.
    - retry/failed/delay logic/rate limiting
    
User
  │
  ▼
POST /signup
  │
  ├── Save user
  ├── Add email job to BullMQ
  └── Return response (200ms)

Requirements

- GET THE PROBLEMS
- GET ONE PROBLEMS
- POST A SUBMISSION FOR A PROBLEMS
- SEE RESULT (SUCCESS/ERROR)`

